#Scope
  Package Scope -- All declaration has to start with a key word, eg package, var, func
  	all declared funcs are visible in the same package.
		func name has to be unique within the same package.
		*variables decalred in package scope live forever, until program exists.
	  to make a variable or a func visible to other packages, make its first letter uppercase.
    
  Block Scope
		variables declared in a func is only visible to the code inside the func.

  File Scope
		imported packages are only visible to the importing file
		
		-- renaming imported packages
		import f "fmt"
